","tid":1180762,"uid":35790,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"51d42ae40376b7fda475b5ff2c98abb69bd9732a","tid":1180762,"uid":16777,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:54:06.000Z","msg":"咩叫退將 完全理解唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:58:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/twapple/640pix/20161116/LA12/LA12_001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2Ftwapple%2F640pix%2F20161116%2FLA12%2FLA12_001.jpg&h=7049883b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n32位退將 藍營大老  聞中國國歌起立"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:05:06.000Z","msg":"早40年前蔣經國捉晒呢32個去鎗決啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:07:18.000Z","msg":"早40年呢班人根本唔會有呢個機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a65d81fcec07a85aa3328ca5302a2e0aecfced","tid":1180762,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ec0137dc1a59099ca89f65e2ce60a22088fce2e1","tid":1180762,"uid":50144,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"7a861a2404ebb9638ef06b86f31d47e271cb6229","tid":1180762,"uid":34517,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"cf36685035d9ce7ec1f54dd9de163e57350b4f68","tid":1180762,"uid":35790,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:58:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/twapple/640pix/20161116/LA12/LA12_001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2Ftwapple%2F640pix%2F20161116%2FLA12%2FLA12_001.jpg&h=7049883b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n32位退將 藍營大老  聞中國國歌起立"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:05:06.000Z","msg":"早40年前蔣經國捉晒呢32個去鎗決啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:07:18.000Z","msg":"早40年呢班人根本唔會有呢個機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"國民黨拒朝野協商「退將叛國條款」最快31日立法 最重剝奪全退俸<br />\n<br />\n2019.05.30<br />\n<br />\n內政委員會朝野協商決議國安法逕送院會，最快明日三讀過關重懲退將叛國行為剝奪退俸。<br />\n <br />\n退將未來從事共諜叛國行為，恐將遭剝奪全部退俸？立院內政委員會今（30日）預計朝野協商討論相關國安法案，因國民黨立委無人出席、拒審國安法修正案，主席洪宗熠決議將修正法案逕送院會處理，因本週五為立法院第9屆第7會期最後一天，最快將於明日3讀立法。<br />\n<br />\n因退將吳斯懷等人赴中國唱中共國歌，引發輿論爭議。為反制國軍退將到中國從事共諜叛國等行為，林俊憲等人擬《國家安全法》第5條之1條文修正草；王定宇、劉世芳等人擬具《國家安全法》第2條之1及第5條之1條文修正草案等案，明文規定叛國行為判刑定讞將剝奪所有退俸，今在內政委員會進入朝野協商階段。<br />\n<br />\n不過開會不久後，因國民黨立委不願進行朝野協商，主席洪宗熠宣告散會，並將相關法案逕送院會處理。根據王定宇提案說明，這次國安法修正將處理發展中共組織階段，加重共諜刑責、沒入犯罪資金與器具；已退國軍人員，退休後從事共諜叛國行為，判刑定讞者，也將剝奪全部退休給與。<br />\n<br />\n另外，將中國、港、澳及境外敵對勢力將列入國安法修正，並將「網路」納入國安法管轄範圍，今決議也逕送院會處理。攸關公投法是否納身分證驗證的「公投法部分條文草案」明也將進入院會審議。<br />\n<a href=\"https://fountmedia.io/article/16523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffountmedia.io%2Farticle%2F16523&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=6976b8c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://fountmedia.io/article/16523</a>"},{"pid":"4add8ea00f3dc6531722fbd018dd041d630a2985","tid":1180762,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa820093e4e76e2da71fa8c7a1f09c71a69b736","tid":1180762,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:43:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7773bb485a485ff5428272292511a8dbf2789350","tid":1180762,"uid":2654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7a861a2404ebb9638ef06b86f31d47e271cb6229","tid":1180762,"uid":34517,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"cf36685035d9ce7ec1f54dd9de163e57350b4f68","tid":1180762,"uid":35790,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"51d42ae40376b7fda475b5ff2c98abb69bd9732a","tid":1180762,"uid":16777,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:54:06.000Z","msg":"咩叫退將 完全理解唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:58:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/twapple/640pix/20161116/LA12/LA12_001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2Ftwapple%2F640pix%2F20161116%2FLA12%2FLA12_001.jpg&h=7049883b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n32位退將 藍營大老  聞中國國歌起立"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:05:06.000Z","msg":"早40年前蔣經國捉晒呢32個去鎗決啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:45:11.000Z","msg":"40年前佢地出門去北京之前已經送呿去綠島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed2c811da1d76feef211a4875639bceccddb73a","tid":1180762,"uid":56147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:46:53.000Z","msg":"如果係美國邊敢  就係台灣先敢     台狗左膠"},{"pid":"d9704633a88d487e5bf681c7c7c8c74f0a28b559","tid":1180762,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:55:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}